                <p>
                    <hi rend="color(#000000)">Beyond the authors of this poster proposal, we would like to acknowledge the role of the work package leads: Maciej Eder (coordinator), Justin Tonra, Christof Schöch, Karina van Dalen-Oskam, Carolin Odebrecht, Matej Ďurčo, Peer Trilcke, Frank Fischer, Julie M. </hi>
                    <hi rend="color(#000000)">Birkholz, Marco Raciti. Find out more about the team here: </hi>
                    <ptr target="https://clsinfra.io/about/ourresearchers/"/>
                    <hi rend="color(#000000)">. </hi>
                </p>
            </div>
